<section id="specialties" class="scroll-mt-16 mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">My Specialties</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-400">
            These are the styles of photography I’m most drawn to—from timeless black and white images to nature, animals, and moments captured along the way.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-4">
        <div class="card overflow-hidden">
            <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden">
                <img class="h-full w-full object-cover transition duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02]"
                     src="images/winter.jpg" alt="Black & White" />
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold">Black & White</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-400">Black and white photography allows me to focus on light, contrast, and emotion. Without color, the textures
                    and quiet details of a moment often become even more powerful.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card overflow-hidden">
            <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden">
                <img class="h-full w-full object-cover transition duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02]"
                     src="images/gotgsnow.jpeg" alt="Nature & Landscape" />
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold">Nature & Landscape</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-400">Nature offers endless beauty to explore. From wide landscapes to small details, I enjoy capturing the peaceful
                    and ever-changing scenes found outdoors.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card overflow-hidden">
            <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden">
                <img class="h-full w-full object-cover transition duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02]"
                     src="images/dogs.jpg" alt="Animals & Wildlife" />
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold">Animals & Wildlife</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-400">Animals have a personality all their own. I love capturing their character, curiosity, and the natural moments
                    that make each one unique.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card overflow-hidden">
            <div class="aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden">
                <img class="h-full w-full object-cover transition duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02]"
                     src="images/chicago.jpg" alt="Travel" />
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
                <h3 class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold">Travel</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-400">Travel photography allows me to document the places I visit and the stories within them—from cities and streets to
                    people, landmarks, and quiet moments along the way.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

